A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdunkin-vs-dutch-bros-coffee-which-is-better-photos-review-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20went%20to%20Dunkin'%20and%20Dutch%20Bros%20Coffee%20and%20ordered%20drinks%20like%20vanilla%20cold%20brews%2C%20chai%20lattes%2C%20and%20mochas%20to%20see%20which%20chain%20does%20it%20best.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Meredith%20Schneider)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdunkin-vs-dutch-bros-coffee-which-is-better-photos-review-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Astronauts%2C%20Set%20For%20Space%20Mission%2C%20Touch%20Down%20In%20US%20For%20Training%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Gaganyatri's%20or%20astronaut%20designates%20set%20to%20fly%20to%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS)%20have%20reached%20the%20United%20States%20and%20joined%20their%20training%20at%20Houston%20based%20American%20commercial%20company%20Axiom%20Space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20has%20assigned%20Group%20Captain%20Shubhanshu%20Shukla%20and%20Group%20Captain%20Prasanth%20Balakrishnan%20Nair%20-%20part%20of%20India's%20Gaganyaan%20Mission%20-%20for%20training%20at%20Axiom%20Space%20and%20NASA's%20Kennedy%20Space%20Center%20and%20SpaceX.%20While%20Group%20Captain%20Shukla%20is%20the%20primary%20astronaut%20for%20the%20Axiom%20mission%2C%20Group%20Captain%20Nair%20is%20the%20back-up%20astronaut%20for%20the%20project.%20The%20upcoming%20flight%20is%20designated%20as%20the%20Axiom-4%20(Ax-4)%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAxiom%20Space%20said%20the%20two%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20test%20pilots%20have%20joined%20the%20astronaut%20training%20regimen%20that%20may%20last%20several%20months%20before%20the%20flight%20to%20ISS%20in%202025.%20It%20also%20confirmed%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bcrew%20is%20expected%20to%20spend%20up%20to%2014%20days%20on%20the%20space%20station%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20Axiom%20Space%20said%20%26quot%3BAxiom-4%20will%20launch%20to%20the%20orbiting%20laboratory%20aboard%20a%20SpaceX%20Falcon%209%20rocket%20and%20Dragon%20spacecraft%20from%20Florida.%26quot%3B%20No%20launch%20date%20has%20been%20disclosed%20just%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ax-4%20crewmembers%20begin%20training%20with%20Axiom%20Space%2C%20NASA%2C%20and%20SpaceX.%20The%20crew%20assigned%20to%20Ax-4%20includes%20American%20astronaut%20Commander%20Peggy%20Whitson%2C%20Mission%20Pilot%20Shubhanshu%20Shukla%20of%20India%2C%20Mission%20Specialist%20Slawosz%20Uznanski%20of%20European%20Space%20Agency%20(ESA)%2FPoland%2C%20and%20Mission%20Specialist%20Tibor%20Kapu%20of%20Hungary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20be%20the%20fourth%20commercial%20crew%20program%20spearheaded%20by%20Axiom%20Space%20and%20%26quot%3BAx-4%20represents%20Axiom%20Space's%20continued%20efforts%20to%20build%20opportunity%20for%20countries%20to%20research%2C%20innovate%2C%20test%2C%20and%20engage%20with%20people%20around%20the%20world%20while%20in%20low-Earth%20orbit%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Michael%20Suffredini%2C%20CEO%20of%20Axiom%20Space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20mission%20broadens%20horizons%20for%20nations%20with%20ambitious%20goals%20of%20advancing%20scientific%2C%20technological%2C%20and%20economic%20pursuits.%20Our%20collaboration%20with%20ESA%20for%20a%20second%20time%20and%20the%20inclusion%20of%20Hungary%20and%20India%20underscores%20Axiom%20Space's%20ability%20to%20cultivate%20global%20partners%2C%20expand%20the%20scope%20of%20exploration%2C%20and%20open%20up%20new%20avenues%20to%20grow%20a%20global%20space%20economy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20trained%20biochemist%20and%20America's%20most%20experienced%20astronaut%2C%2064-year-old%20Dr%20Peggy%20Annette%20Whitson%2C%20is%20the%20designated%20Commander%20of%20the%20Axiom-4%20mission%20on%20which%20Group%20Captain%20Shubhanshu%20Shukla%2C%2039%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20fly%20to%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20in%20early%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Whitson%20is%20a%20veteran%20of%20four%20flights%20to%20space%20and%20while%20she%20retired%20as%20a%20NASA%20astronaut%20in%202018%2C%20she%20now%20works%20for%20Axiom%20Space%2C%20the%20Houston-based%20private%20space%20company%2C%20where%20she%20is%20the%20director%20of%20the%20human%20space%20flight%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAxiom%20Space%20describes%20Dr%20Whitson%20as%20%26quot%3BAmerica's%20most%20experienced%20astronaut%2C%20who%20flew%20on%20three%20NASA%20long-duration%20space%20flights%20and%20Axiom%20Mission%202%20(Ax-2)%2C%20accumulating%20675%20days%20in%20space%2C%20more%20than%20any%20other%20American%20astronaut%20or%20woman%20astronaut%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20look%20forward%20to%20commanding%20my%20second%20commercial%20human%20spaceflight%20mission%20with%20Axiom%20Space%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Peggy%20Whitson%2C%20Ax-4%20commander.%20%26quot%3BWith%20a%20culturally%20diverse%20crew%2C%20we%20are%20not%20only%20advancing%20scientific%20knowledge%20but%20also%20fostering%20international%20collaboration%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAxiom%20Space%20is%20confident%20of%20pulling%20of%20the%20mission%20for%20which%20India%20has%20paid%20to%20acquire%20this%20astronaut%20seat.%20It%20says%20Axiom%20Mission%201%20was%20the%20first%20all-private%20mission%20to%20the%20space%20station%2C%20Axiom%20Mission%202%20launched%20the%20first%20Saudi%20female%20to%20space%2C%20and%20Axiom%20Mission%203%20included%20both%20the%20first%20Turkish%20astronaut%20and%20first%20ESA%20astronaut%20to%20fly%20on%20a%20commercial%20space%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhitson%20says%20%26quot%3Bnow%2C%20with%20Ax-4%2C%20we%20ascend%20even%20higher%2C%20bringing%20even%20more%20nations%20to%20low-Earth%20orbit%20and%20expanding%20humanity's%20reach%20among%20the%20stars.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722863160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024