se%2C%20the%20Vice%20President%20explained%20that%20there%20is%20a%20provision%20to%20change%20the%20name%20that%20appears%20on%20the%20election%20certificate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bentire%20country%20is%20proud%26quot%3B%20of%20Amitabh%20Bachchan's%20achievement%2C%20Chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20Jaya%20Ji%2C%20the%20name%20that%20appears%20in%20the%20election%20certificate%20is%20what%20is%20used%2C%20and%20you%20can%20get%20the%20name%20changed%3B%20there%20is%20a%20provision%20for%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SP%20MP%20also%20questioned%20why%20Union%20Minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20did%20not%20add%20his%20wife's%20name%20after%20his.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20which%2C%20Khattar%20sarcastically%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20for%20my%20wife's%20name%20in%20front%20of%20mine...%20not%20in%20this%20birth%20(since%20Khattar%20is%20unmarried)%3B%20for%20this%2C%20you%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20until%20the%20next%20birth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20SP%20MP's%20earlier%20objection%20to%20being%20addressed%20as%20%26quot%3BJaya%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%26quot%3B%20by%20Deputy%20Chairman%20Harivansh%20Narayan%20Singh%20during%20the%20House%20proceedings%20on%20July%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaya%20Bachchan%20objected%20by%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BSir%2C%20only%20Jaya%20Bachchan%20would%20have%20sufficed%2C%26quot%3B%20stressing%20her%20unease%20about%20women%20being%20identified%20only%20by%20their%20husband's%20names%20as%20if%20%26quot%3Bthey%20don't%20have%20their%20own%20identity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20supplementary%20question%2C%20the%20actor-turned-politician%20asked%3A%20%26quot%3BFormer%20Haryana%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20here.%20Gurgaon%20was%20declared%20a%20smart%20city%2C%20but%20recently%2C%20the%20water%20was%20logged%20up%20to%20the%20waist%20there.%20I%20wanted%20to%20go%20there%20for%20some%20work%20but%20was%20un