some%20time%20now%2C%20there%20have%20been%20growing%20concerns%20that%20the%20technology's%20ability%20to%20deliver%20on%20the%20hype%20has%20been%20a%20tad%20overestimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goldmansachs.com%2Finsights%2Ftop-of-mind%2Fgen-ai-too-much-spend-too-little-benefit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%20some%20probing%20research%20toward%20the%20end%20of%20June%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20posed%20the%20question%20investors%20have%20spent%20the%20past%20week%20doubling%20down%20on%20during%20earnings%20calls%3A%20%26quot%3BToo%20much%20spend%2C%20too%20little%20benefit%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20conclusions%20were%20at%20odds%20with%20what%20Silicon%20Valley%20CEOs%20spent%20much%20of%20last%20week%20telling%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJim%20Covello%2C%20Goldman's%20head%20of%20global%20equity%20research%2C%20suggested%20AI%20%26quot%3Bmust%20be%20able%20to%20solve%20complex%20problems%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bearn%20an%20adequate%20return%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20roughly%20%241%20trillion%20needed%20to%20develop%20and%20run%20it.%20In%20his%20view%2C%20in%20vogue%2C%20generative%20models%20simply%20aren't%20built%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaron%20Acemoglu%2C%20an%20MIT%20professor%20and%20economist%20the%20bank%20interviewed%20as%20part%20of%20the%20research%2C%20also%20sounded%20skeptical%2C%20with%20his%20prediction%20that%20AI%20will%20affect%20fewer%20than%205%25%20of%20all%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%2C%20which%20briefly%20became%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20company%20thanks%20to%20nonstop%20demand%20for%20the%20chips%20it%20supplies%20to%20AI%20model%20makers%2C%20won't%20report%20earnings%20until%20the%20end%20of%20August.%20Yet%20it's%20found%20itself%20unable%20to%20escape%20the%20panic%20spreading%20in%20the%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e5f92224-5911-4124-9402-35324de4aad4%5C%22%3E'Overhyped'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chip%20company%20showed%20its%20first%20major%20sign%20of%20weakness%20last%20week%20after%20The%20Information%20reported%20that%20a%20design%20flaw%20would%20delay%20the%20production%20of%20its%20newest%20chip%2C%20the%20Blackwell%20B200%2C%20by%20at%20least%20three%20months.%20That's%20bad%20news%20for%20Meta%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Microsoft%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20which%20have%20put%20in%20huge%20orders%20for%20the%20powerful%20new%20chip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20hedge%20fund%20Elliott%20Management%20has%20been%20busy%20telling%20investors%20that%20Nvidia%20is%20%26quot%3Boverhyped%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Financial%20Times%20reported%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20others%20really%20start%20to%20believe%20that's%20the%20case%2C%20it%20could%20mark%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20end%20for%20the%20AI%20rally.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20some%20remain%20hopeful%20that%20it's%20just%20a%20passing%20phase.%20In%20a%20research%20note%20on%20Monday%2C%20Wedbush%20analyst%20Dan%20Ives%20wrote%20that%20despite%20investors%20%26quot%3Bfeeling%20massive%20pain%20globally%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20message%20to%20those%20wondering%20if%20this%20%26quot%3Btech%20bull%20market%20and%20historic%20run%20for%20tech%20stocks%20is%20over%26quot%3B%20was%20clear%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20NOT%20in%20our%20view%20and%20this%20is%20just%20a%20white%20knuckle%20moment%20in%20a%20multi-year%20bull%20run%20for%20tech%20stocks%20that%20need%20hand-holding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20its%20current%20trajectory%2C%20though%2C%20AI%20hype%20looks%20ready%20to%20make%20a%20violent%20return%20to%20reality.%20Investors%20better%20brace%20themselves%20for%20the%20full%20force%20of%20the%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-boom-faces-crash-landing-stock-market-selloff-nvidia-microsoft-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722862134000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22h