0forefathers%20chose%20democracy%20as%20the%20path%20forward%2C%20aiming%20to%20rebuild%20a%20nation%20that%20could%20become%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20the%20world.%20This%20vision%20was%20made%20possible%20by%20our%20visionary%20leaders%20and%20architects%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20who%20were%20dedicated%20to%20creating%20institutions%20capable%20of%20keeping%20the%20country%20united%20even%20in%20the%20most%20challenging%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20democracy%20stands%20as%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20achievements%20of%20the%2020th%20century.%20For%20the%20past%2075%20years%2C%20we%20have%20upheld%20and%20defended%20democratic%20ideals%20with%20resilience.%20Our%20institutions%20have%20acted%20as%20fundamental%20supports%20for%20maintaining%20our%20democratic%20framework.%20Yet%2C%20the%20present%20situation%20in%20Delhi%20represents%20a%20serious%20threat%20to%20the%20core%20of%20Indian%20democracy.%20The%20chaos%2C%20mismanagement%2C%20and%20upheaval%20in%20Delhi's%20governance%20-%20resulting%20from%20the%20central%20government's%20intervention%20via%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20(L-G)%20-%20endanger%20all%20that%20we%20have%20accomplished%2C%20putting%20the%20very%20spirit%20of%20Indian%20democracy%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuestions%20Of%20A%20Delhi%20Voter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20value%20of%20every%20vote%20in%20Goa%20with%201.2%20million%20voters%20is%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20Delhi%20with%2020%20million%20voters.%20As%20a%20Delhi%20voter%2C%20I%20feel%20it%20is%20my%20responsibility%20to%20highlight%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20voters%20of%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20whose%20votes%20seem%20devalued%20by%20the%20intentional%20degradation%20and%20attempted%20killing%20of%20democracy.%20The%20chaos%20and%20mismanagement%20caused%20by%20the%20Central%20government%20through%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20(L-G)%20are%20severely%20affecting%20the%20people%20-%20the%20true%20masters%20in%20a%20democracy%20-%20and%20undermining%20the%20concept%20of%20the%20triple%20chain%20of%20accountability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocracy%20is%20both%20a%20form%20of%20government%20and%20a%20way%20of%20life%20that%20upholds%20liberty%20and%20equality.%20It%20is%20rooted%20in%20philosophical%20principles%2C%20and%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Delhi%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20think%20beyond%20traditional%20definitions%20of%20democracy.%20Consider%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20and%20far-reaching%20consequences%20of%20denying%20equal%20political%20rights.%20The%20original%20Greek%20word%20'demokratia'%20means%20the%20people%20(%3Cem%3Edemos%3C%2Fem%3E)%20rule%20(%3Cem%3Ekratos%3C%2Fem%3E).%20But%20in%20Delhi%2C%20who%20are%20the%20people%2C%20and%20how%20do%20they%20rule%3F%20What%20happens%20when%20democracy%20becomes%20a%20struggle%20between%20the%20people%20and%20the%20system%20-%20%26quot%3BLok%26quot%3B%20versus%20%26quot%3BTantra%26quot%3B%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20emerged%20from%20the%202011%20anti-corruption%20movement.%20Led%20by%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20a%20Magsaysay%20Awardee%2C%20an%20IITian%20and%20a%20former%20bureaucrat%2C%20the%20AAP%20formed%20a%20government%20with%20outside%20support%20from%20Congress%20in%202013%20after%20winning%2028%20seats%20in%20its%20first%20election.%20The%20political%20landscape%20changed%20when%20Kejriwal%20challenged%20the%20upcoming%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20Varanasi%20in%202014%20and%20later%20won%20the%202015%20Delhi%20Assembly%20Elections%20with%20a%20record%20number%20of%20seats.%20This%20is%20when%20PM%20Modi%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20struggling%20to%20gain%20a%20foothold%20in%20Delhi%2C%20began%20to%20thwart%20Kejriwal%20by%20any%20means%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFighting%20For%20Control%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20hurdles%20created%20by%20the%20central%20government%20through%20the%20L-G%2C%20the%20AAP's%20governance%2C%20especially%20in%20education%2C%20healthcare%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20electricity%2C%20has%20been%20widely%20praised.%20The%20people%20of%20Delhi%20re-elected%20AAP%20with%20a%20thumping%20majority%20in%202020%20and%20again%20in%20the%20recent%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20Elections.%20However%2C%20the%20situation%20deteriorated%20significantly%20after%20the%20Centre%20passed%20the%20Delhi%20Services%20Act%202023%2C%20stripping%20the%20elected%20government%20of%20control%20over%20the%20bureaucracy%20and%20overturning%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20Constitutional%20Bench%20verdict.%20The%20Constitution%20bench%20had%20emphasised%20federalism%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20democratically%20elected%20government%20is%20not%20provided%20with%20the%20power%20to%20control%20the%20officers%20posted%20within%20its%20domain%2C%20then%20the%20principle%20underlying%20the%20triple-chain%20of%20collective%20responsibility%20would%20become%20redundant.%20That%20is%20to%20say%2C%20if%20the%20government%20is%20not%20able%20to%20control%20and%20hold%20to%20account%20the%20officers%20posted%20in%20its%20service%2C%20then%20its%20responsibility%20towards%20the%20legislature%20as%20well%20as%20the%20public%20is%20diluted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20government%20can%20function%20without%20control%20over%20its%20officers.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20L-G%20have%20weaponised%20the%20bureaucracy%20to%20bring%20the%20administration%20to%20a%20standstill.%20The%20Delhi%20government%20has%20challenged%20the%20Act%2C%20and%20it%20was%20referred%20to%20a%20Constitutional%20Bench%20in%20July%202023.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20yet%20to%20notify%20the%20Bench%2C%20adversely%20affecting%20Delhi%20residents%20as%20if%20punishing%20them%20for%20electing%20a%20party%20of%20their%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdministration%20In%20Suspension%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Services%20Act%202023%20has%20thrown%20governance%20into%20chaos.%20Routine%20administrative%20tasks%20have%20stalled%2C%20including%20payments%20for%20Mohalla%20Clinics%2C%20the%20Farishtey%20Scheme%2C%20doorstep%20delivery%20of%20services%2C%20the%20removal%20of%20bus%20marshals%2C%20abrupt%20halts%20in%20old-age%20pensions%2C%20and%20the%20withholding%20of%20proposals%20like%20sending%20teachers%20to%20Finland%20for%20training.%20Hundreds%20of%20such%20hurdles%20created%20by%20the%20Central%20government%20disrupt%20Delhi's%20administration.%20Even%20the%20desilting%20of%20roads%20is%20not%20being%20carried%20out%20despite%20instructions%20from%20ministers%2C%20no%20third-party%20audits%20are%20conducted%2C%20and%20disciplinary%20action%20is%20not%20taken%20against%20officials.%20This%20negligence%20recently%20caused%20the%20deaths%20of%20three%20UPSC%20aspirants%20in%20Rajinder%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202023%20Constitution%20Bench%20judgment%20emphasised%20that%20people%20are%20the%20ultimate%20sovereign%2C%20and%20the%20executive%20is%20accountable%20to%20the%20public%20through%20the%20%26quot%3Btriple%20chain%20of%20accountability%26quot%3B.%20This%20means%20voters%20elect%20their%20representatives%2C%20who%20formulate%20policies%2C%20and%20civil%20servants%20implement%20them.%20Civil%20servants%20should%20answer%20to%20ministers%2C%20who%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20answer%20to%20the%20voters.%20But%20in%20Delhi%2C%20civil%20servants%20are%20not%20accountable%20to%20the%20ministers%2C%20meaning%20Delhi's%20electorate%20has%20no%20control%20over%20the%20policies%20implemented%20in%20their%20constituencies.%20This%20was%20precisely%20what%20the%20court%20addressed%20when%20it%20ruled%20that%20Delhi's%20civil%20servants%20must%20be%20accountable%20to%20the%20Delhi%20government%20they%20serve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Value%20Does%20A%20Vote%20Hold%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20remains%3A%20What%20are%20Delhi%20voters%20being%20punished%20for%3F%20Do%20they%20deserve%20this%3F%20What%20value%20does%20their%20vote%20hold%3F%20What%20message%20are%20we%20sending%20from%20Delhi%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20democracy%2C%20to%20the%20world%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20hope%20that%20Indian%20democracy%20will%20emerge%20stronger%20from%20this%20dark%20phase%20and%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20beacon%20for%20the%20world%2C%20I%20conclude%20with%20the%20poignant%20lines%20of%20revolutionary%20poet%20Sahir%20Ludhianvi%2C%20dedicated%20to%20those%20in%20power%20undermining%20democracy%20in%20India%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EZulm%20phir%20zulm%20hai%20badht%C4%81%20hai%20to%20mit%20jaata%20hai%3Cbr%3E%5CnKhoon%20phir%20khoon%20hai%20tapkeg%C4%81%20to%20jam%20jaega%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E(Anurag%20Mishra%20is%20a%20governance%20Specialist%20and%20an%20AAP%20supporter)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722861960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F8oh2sn98_delhi_625x300_05_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdelhi-and-its-battle-of-lok-vs-tantra-6268218%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20Delhi%20voter%2C%20I%20feel%20it%20is%20my%20responsibility%20to%20highlight%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20voters%20of%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20whose%20votes%20seem%20devalued%20by%20the%20intentional%20degradation%20and%20attempted%20killing%20of%20democracy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdelhi-and-its-battle-of-lok-vs-tantra-6268218%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdelhi-and-its-battle-of-lok-vs-tantra-6268218%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdelhi-and-its-battle-of-lok-vs-tantra-626