ial%20interests%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20will%20hurt%20us%20all%2C%20especially%20through%20more%20dangerous%20roads%2C%20a%20higher%20risk%20of%20addiction%20among%20our%20youth%2C%20and%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-ron-desantis-failed-presidential-campaign-border-security-social-media-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincrease%20in%20crime%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGriffin%20wrote%20that%20%26quot%3Bskyrocketing%20crime%2C%20suffering%20among%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ba%20decline%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20in%20Florida's%20vibrant%20neighborhoods%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20inevitable%20if%20Amendment%203%20passed%2C%20citing%20similar%20initiatives%20in%20California%2C%20Colorado%2C%20and%20New%20York%20that%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bmistakes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202022%20study%20published%20in%20the%20Journal%20of%20Studies%20on%20Alcohol%20and%20Drugs%20found%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flegal-marijuana-states-2018-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegalization%20of%20recreational%20marijuana%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20linked%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20traffic%20crashes%20and%20fatalities.%20However%2C%20research%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.colorado.edu%2Ftoday%2F2023%2F01%2F24%2Fgateway-drug-no-more-study-shows-legalizing-recreational-cannabis-does-not-increase%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUniversity%20of%20Colorado%20Boulder%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20legalized%20recreational%20cannabis%20did%20not%20correlate%20with%20an%20increase%20in%20substance-use%20disorders%20or%20use%20of%20other%20drugs%20among%20adults%20and%20found%20no%20link%20to%20increases%20in%20cognitive%2C%20psychological%2C%20social%2C%20relationship%2C%20or%20financial%20problems.%20Meta-analyses%20comparing%20the%20results%20of%20multiple%20studies%C2%A0regarding%20the%20impact%20of%20marijuana%20legalization%20on%20crime%