0keep%20calm%20and%20help%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hasina%2C%20who%20has%20ruled%20Bangladesh%20since%202009%2C%20had%20defied%20weeks%20of%20demands%20for%20her%20to%20stand%20down%20but%20fled%20following%20a%20brutal%20day%20of%20unrest%20on%20Sunday%20in%20which%20nearly%20100%20people%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtests%20broke%20out%20over%20the%20reintroduction%20of%20a%20quota%20scheme%20that%20reserved%20more%20than%20half%20of%20all%20government%20jobs%20for%20certain%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20escalated%20despite%20the%20scheme%20having%20been%20scaled%20back%20by%20Bangladesh's%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20hugely%20symbolic%20rebuke%20of%20Ms%20Hasina%2C%20a%20former%20army%20chief%20demanded%20the%20government%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%26quot%3B%20withdraw%20troops%20and%20allow%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20anti-government%20movement%20had%20attracted%20people%20from%20across%20society%20in%20the%20South%20Asian%20nation%20of%20about%20170%20million%20people%2C%20including%20film%20stars%2C%20musicians%20and%20singers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2076-year-old%20prime%20minister%20fled%20the%20country%20by%20helicopter%2C%20say%20reports%2C%20shortly%20after%20protesters%20had%20stormed%20her%20palace%20in%20Dhaka.%20Multiple%20reports%20say%20she%20is%20headed%20to%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh's%20Channel%2024%20broadcast%20images%20of%20crowds%20running%20into%20the%20compound%2C%20waving%20to%20the%20camera%20as%20they%20celebrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOthers%20smashed%20a%20statues%20of%20Hasina's%20father%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahma%2C%20the%20country's%20independence%20hero.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hasina%20and%20won%20her%20fourth%20consecutive%20election%20in%20January%20after%20a%20vote%20without%20genuine%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20AFP%20Inputs)%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A