Fstory%2Famp%2Fimane-khelif-boxer-at-centre-of-olympic-gender-row-says-winning-gold-would-be-best-response-13191156%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fimane-khelif-boxer-at-centre-of-olympic-gender-row-says-winning-gold-would-be-best-response-13191156%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Couple%20Uses%203D-Printed%20Claws%20%26amp%3B%20Jaws%20to%20Save%20Arunachal%E2%80%99s%20Endangered%20Wildlife%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20every%20person%20who%20dresses%20from%20head%20to%20toe%20in%20traditional%20tribal%20attire%2C%20five%20animals%20are%20killed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Nabam%20Bapu%20(29)%20relays%20this%20to%20me%2C%20his%20sadness%20at%20this%20harsh%20reality%20is%20evident.%20Throughout%20his%20growing-up%20years%2C%20the%20civil%20engineer%20was%20proud%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F326047%2Fassam-zankla-studio-sell-eco-friendly-cultural-heritage-toys-bodo-community-tribes-barbie-dolls%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erich%20cultural%20traditions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20included%20the%20festive%20attire%20donned%20by%20his%20Nyishi%20tribe%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%2026%20major%20tribes%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20he%20grew%20older%2C%20he%20understood%20how%20animal%20parts%20constituted%20a%20major%20chunk%20of%20the%20attire.%20The%20irony%20of%20animals%20being%20poached%20even%20as%20their%20numbers%20are%20on%20a%20constant%20decline%20was%20unsettling%20for%20Nabam.%20Innocent%20animals%20were%20being%20slaughtered%20for%20aesthetic%20reasons%2C%20he%20deduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20probing%20of%20his%20tribe%E2%80%99s%20motivations%20led%20him%20to%20understand%20that%20he%20was%20wrong.%20The%20parts%20held%20cultural%20significance.%20But%2C%20to%20Nabam%2C%20the%20end%20did%20not%20justify%20the%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%2