a.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftribes-2-1722419872-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftribes-2-1722419872-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftribes-2-1722419872-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359175%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20beak%20of%20the%20Great%20Indian%20Hornbill%20is%20worn%20on%20the%20head%20to%20show%20beauty%20and%20youthfulness%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Nabam%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20of%20the%20Nyishi%20tribe%20love%20their%20accessories.%20The%20men%20wear%20stone%20bead%20necklaces%2C%20%3Cem%3ETesee%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20while%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20necklaces%20are%20called%20%3Cem%3ESeetir%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Both%20terminate%20at%20the%20waistline%2C%20which%20is%20adorned%20with%20a%20belt%20known%20as%20%3Cem%3ETama%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20worn%20by%20men%2C%20while%20women%20wear%20small%20metal%20discs%20called%20%3Cem%3EHupiya%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20garments%2C%20%3Cem%3ETassh%20Nara%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20black%20cloak%20made%20out%20of%20a%20sago%20palm%20tree%E2%80%99s%20blade-like%20skin%20which%20is%20cut%2C%20dried%2C%20and%20then%20tied%20together%20to%20make%20the%20furry%20coat)%2C%20and%20backpacks%2C%20%3Cem%3ENara%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20festooned%20with%20animal%20fur%20too.%20The%20backpack%20contains%20a%20%3Cem%3Edao%20%3C%2Fem%3E(machete)%2C%20a%20sword%20whose%20cover%20is%20made%20of%20monkey%20skin%2C%20a%20spear%2C%20and%20arrows.%20The%20backpack%20is%20slung%20across%20the%20shoulder%20by%20a%20strap%20made%20of%20bearskin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20jewellery%20meanwhile%20includes%20tiger%20nails%2C%20jaws%20of%20the%20tiger%20and%20clouded%20leopard%20%E2%80%94%20both%20%E2%80%98vulnerable%E2%80%99%20according%20to%20the%20IUCN%2C%20and%20teeth%20of%20the%20wild%20boar.%20N