ated%20cultivator%20that%20helps%20%E2%80%9Cgrow%20your%20own%20vitamins%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Snehal%20Ambekar%20and%20Sayak%20Gupta%2C%20two%20food%20technologists%2C%20devised%20a%20portable%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349300%2Fhow-to-grow-microgreens-at-home-or-farm-aditi-mali-of-mali-greens-shares-tips%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoilless%20microgreens%20cultivator%20%3C%2Fa%3Elabelled%20%E2%80%98Half%20Inch%20Garden%E2%80%99%20through%20their%20venture%20SS%20AgriQulture%20Innovations.%20What%20sets%20this%20cultivator%20apart%20is%20that%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20require%20any%20seeds.%20Instead%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20seed%20patches%20made%20from%20agricultural%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20friends%20are%20now%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20make%20growing%20superfoods%20convenient%20and%20accessible%20for%20everyone.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20their%20journey%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20garden%20that%20fits%20on%20your%20coffee%20table!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Snehal%20Ambekar%20was%20just%2017%2C%20she%20faced%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295026%2Fhealthcare-startup-to-manage-pcos-for-indian-women-by-sisters-raises-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultitude%20of%20health%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20felt%20dizzy%20when%20she%20stood%20up%2C%20had%20blackouts%2C%20brain%20fog%2C%20sleep%20arthritis%2C%20and%20an%20overwhelming%20sense%20of%20fatigue.%20Things%20were%20so%20bad%20that%20this%20young%20girl%20was%20bedridden.%20She%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20focus%20on%20her%20studies%20or%20even%20step%20out%20of%20the%20house.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20during%20the%20advent%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20and%20since%20some%20of%20her%20symptoms%20matched%20with%20COVID-19%2C%20her%20parents%20had%20her%20tested%20for%20it.%20When%20she%20tested%20negative%2C%20the%20doctor%20suggested%20a%20complete%20blood%20checkup%20with%20tests%20%E2%80%94%20including%20thyroid%2C%20diabetes%2C%20iron%2C%20serum%20creatinine%2C%20Vitamin%20B12%2C%20D%2C%20B9%2C%20etc.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20some%20X-rays%20and%20the%20result%20was%20clear%3A%20Snehal%20was%20nutritionally%20deficient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teenager%20was%20shocked.%20%E2%80%9CI%20ate%20home-cooked%20vegetarian%20meals%20and%20followed%20a%20healthy%20diet.%20I%20was%20young%2C%20healthy%2C%20and%20exercised%20regularly.%20How%20could%20I%20have%20a%20vitamin%20deficiency%3F%20I%20was%20in%20disbelief%2C%E2%80%9D%20Snehal%20recalls%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20diagnosis%20shed%20light%20on%20an%20often-overlooked%20aspect%20of%20nutrition%3A%20the%20potential%20for%20deficiency%20even%20in%20seemingly%20healthy%20diets.%20Moreover%2C%20her%20condition%20was%20compounded%20by%20a%20diagnosis%20of%20Polycystic%20Ovary%20Syndrome%20(PCOS)%2C%20a%20hormonal%20disorder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20popping%20more%20than%2010%20pills%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20Mumbai%20resident%2C%20who%20was%20then%20given%20a%20battery%20of%20medicines%20for%20different%20vitamin%20deficiencies%20and%20advised%20a%20complete%20overhaul%20in%20her%20diet%2C%20exercise%2C%20and%20overall%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20she%20buried%20herself%20in%20research%20to%20understand%20which%20foods%20were%20nutrient-dense%20and%20aid%20in%20a%20healthy%20life.%20One%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98superfoods%E2%80%99%20she%20found%20at%20this%20time%20was%20microgreens.%20Little%20did%20she%20realise%20then%20that%20she%20would%20be%20launching%20an%20associated%20startup%20with%20her%20classmate%2C%20Sayak%20Gupta%2C%20four%20years%20later!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3