edia.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-3-1722403565-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359113%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWithin%20six%20months%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20revived%20the%20river%20to%20its%20old%20glory.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManish%20credits%20the%20success%20of%20the%20project%20to%20the%20local%20people%2C%20%3Cem%3Egram%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20MGNREGA%20workers%2C%20and%20district%20officials.%20In%20June%202024%2C%20he%20was%20transferred%20to%20Saharanpur%20district%20but%20this%20did%20not%20affect%20the%20success%20of%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%20Ashish%2C%20the%20District%20Development%20Officer%20of%20Sambhal%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20keep%20monitoring%20for%20encroachments%20and%20ensure%20that%20the%20river%20remains%20rejuvenated.%20Post%20monsoon%2C%20the%20soil%20erodes%20into%20the%20river.%20So%2C%20we%20are%20working%20on%20a%20plan%20to%20organise%20desiltation%20and%20continue%20the%20work%20started%20by%20Manish%20sir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20while%20some%20downstream%20areas%20currently%20have%20water%2C%20they%20expect%20to%20see%20the%20river%20filled%20to%20the%20brim%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20when%20it%20rains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20IAS%20Manish%20was%20reached%20out%20to%20by%20residents%20of%20Saharanpur%20to%20replicate%20the%20work%20seeing%20the%20success%20of%20the%20project%20in%20Sambhal%20district.%20%E2%80%9CSaharanpur%20has%20several%20seasonal%20rivers%20such%20as%20Kali%20and%20Hindon%20rivers.%20They%20originate%20from%20Shivaliks%20and%20pass%20through%20the%20district.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20their%20area%20has%20reduced%20in%20size.%20We%20aim%20to%20work%20on%20these%20rivers%20next%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Manish%20believes%20that%20the%20administration%20can%20only%20play%20the%20role%20of%20a%20facilitator%2C%20but%20it%20is%20only%20when%20the%20community%20becomes%20the%20protector%20of%20its%20rivers%20that%20they%20can%20remain%20rejuvenated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Manish%2C%20the%20Sot%20river%20rejuvenation%20project%20during%20his%20tenure%20in%20Sambhal%20was%20extremely%20fulfilling.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20project%20was%20very%20close%20to%20my%20heart.%20Projects%20such%20as%20river%20rejuvenation%20take%20a%20backseat%20as%20they%20are%20not%20always%20a%20priority%20among%20other%20routine%20works.%20But%20if%20we%20do%20not%20rejuvenate%20these%20rivers%2C%20people%20will%20face%20the%20brunt%20of%20a%20water%20crisis.%20Thankfully%2C%20the%20State%20Government%20has%20also%20been%20actively%20focusing%20on%20the%20environment%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F230547%2Fias-hero-kalyani-river-cleanup-uttar-pradesh-lockdown-jobs-methods-workers-inspiring-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereviving%20water%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20establishing%20Amrit%20Sarovar%20projects%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Ram%20Ashish.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722426607000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Friver-2-1722402541.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359103%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sot%20River%2C%20once%