2%80%94%20an%20Amritsar-based%20business%20that%20sells%20traditional%20handcrafted%20kitchenware%2C%20dinnerware%2C%20and%20tableware%20made%20of%20brass%2C%20copper%2C%20and%20bronze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20brand%20is%20not%20just%20about%20kitchenware%3B%20it%20is%20also%20dedicated%20to%20helping%20the%20Thathera%20community%20preserve%20the%20art%20of%20making%20these%20utensils%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kirti%20tells%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Her%20company%20recently%20featured%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India%2C%20where%20she%20was%20able%20to%20bag%20an%20%E2%80%98all-shark%E2%80%99%20deal!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20the%20story%20of%20finding%20her%20passion%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20simple%20suggestion%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20me%20choosing%20a%20career%20path%20was%20quite%20difficult.%20Most%20of%20my%20friends%20were%20going%20to%20opt%20for%20engineering%20and%20so%20did%20I.%20But%20soon%20enough%2C%20I%20understood%20that%20it%20was%20not%20for%20me.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20sure%20about%20one%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20different%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kirti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20a%20teacher%20suggested%20that%20she%20try%20something%20more%20artistic%20and%20go%20for%20designing.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20why%2C%20but%20when%20she%20suggested%20it%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20maybe%20it%20was%20indeed%20worth%20a%20try.%20So%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20apply%20to%20Pearl%20Academy.%20Luckily%2C%20I%20got%20in%2C%20and%20it%20paved%20the%20way%20forward%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20to%20think%20more%20creatively%20and%20feel%20that%20I%20was%20where%20I%20belonged.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20second%20year%20in%20training%2C%20she%20worked%20on%20a%20project%20based%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F57220%2Fjourney-indian-handicraft-landscape%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20crafts%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20got%20to%20work%20with%20%3Cem%3EChamba%20Rumal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(an%20embroidered%20handkerchief%20with%20detailed%20patterns%20in%20bright%20and%20pleasing%20colour%20schemes)%20artists%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20riveting%20experience.%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20at%20how%20rich%20the%20handmade%20crafts%20of%20India%20are%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-50-1721396333.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kirit%20Goel%2C%20Founder%20of%20P-TAL%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-50-1721396333.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-50-1721396333-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-50-1721396333-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-50-1721396333-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-50-1721396333-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357791%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKirit%20Goel%2C%20Founder%20of%20P-TAL%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20Kirti%20feels%20that%20the%20project%20was%20the%20key%20foundation%20stone%20that%20paved%20her%20path%20for%20P-TAL.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20to%20research%20more%20crafts%20and%20came%20to%20know%20about%20the%20UNESCO-certified%20craft%2C%20%3Cem%3EThathera%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20art%2C%20I%20found%2C%20was%20disappearing%20as%20there%20was%20not%20much%20demand%20in%20the%20market%20for%20it%20or%20so%20was%20the%20general%20notion%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThathera%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecraft%20involves%20making%20traditional%20brass%20and%20copper%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F281408%2Ftraditional-indian-cookware-clay-cast-iron-brass-copper-amazon-buy-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekitchen%20utensils%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20hand.%20The%20word%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ethathera%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20means%20%E2%80%98the%20beater%E2%80%99%2C%20describing%20the%20act%20of%20beating%20the%20metal%20to%20transform%20it%20into%20desired%20shapes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELearning%20about%20the%20craft%20motivated%20me%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20good%20at%20my%20academy%20but%20I%20knew%20that%20the%20fashion%20market%20was%20highly%20saturated.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20was%20also%20a%20matter%20of%20pride%20for%20me%20to%20save%20the%20dying%20art%20of%20my%20country.%20So%2C%20I%20took%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20and%20lunged%20into%20starting%20P-Tal%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EP-TAL%20was%20founded%20in%202016.%20Talking%20about%20what%20went%20behind%20it%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20things%20first%2C%20I%20got%20started%20on%20the%20market%20research%20and%20kept%20going%20back%20and%20forth%20with%20consultants%20and%20product%20designers%20to%20understand%20what%20the%20consumer%20needs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EConnecting%20with%20craftspersons%20and%20reviving%20the%20art%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20perception%20in%20the%20market%20that%20the%20artisans%20would%20be%20hard%20to%20find%20as%20most%20of%20them%20had%20switched%20careers%2C%20shares%20Kirti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20delved%20deeper%2C%20we%20discovered%20that%20this%20craft%20isn%E2%80%99t%20confined%20to%20just%20one%20location.%20In%20Jaipur%2C%20Moradabad%2C%20Lucknow%2C%20and%20Dehradun%2C%20there%20are%20%3Cem%3EThatheras%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Once%2C%20every%20village%20had%20artisans%20crafting%20brass%20and%20copper%20utensils.%20However%2C%20many%20shifted%20to%20producing%20aluminium%20items%20as%20brass%20and%20copper%20became%20more%20expensive%20and%20demand%20declined.%20The%20artisans%20struggled%20to%20innovate%20with%20these%20materials%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20decline%20in%20the%20traditional%20craft%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CFinding%20artisans%20and%20understanding%20their%20needs%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20difficult.%20We%20identified%20artisans%20and%20collaborated%20with%20them.%E2%80%9D%20Working%20with%20P-TAL%20has%20since%20significantly%20improved%20their%20earnings%20from%20about%20Rs%2020%20per%20hour%20to%20Rs%20150%20per%20hour%2C%20she%20further%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20his%20work%20before%20collaborating%20with%20P-Tal%2C%20Mandeep%20Singh%20(35)%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20hard%20work.%20The%20art%20is%20a%20complex%20process%20that%20involves%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20skilled%20handiwork%2C%20but%20many%20people%20do%20not%20understand%20its%20value.%20Declining%20sales%20led%20to%20less%20and%20less%20work%20each%20year.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20our%20children%20to%20follow%20in%20this%20trade.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20things%20took%20a%20positive%20turn%20three%20years%20ago%20when%20P-Tal%20approached%20him.%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20we%20have%20work%20365%20days%20a%20year.%20P-Tal%20has%20been%20dedicated%20to%20revitalising%20the%20art%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20a%20shift%20towards%20using%20copper%20and%20brass.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20have%20more%20clients%20and%20are%20earning%20better.%20If%20our%20children%20want%20to%20learn%20the%20art%20now%2C%20we%20would%20encourage%20them%2C%20as%20it%20is%20now%20more%20financially%20stable%20than%20ever%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-51-1-1721396562.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20company%20sells%2080%20varieties%20of%20kitchenware%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-51-1-1721396562.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-51-1-1721396562-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-51-1-1721396562-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-51-1-1721396562-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-51-1-1721396562-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357792%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20company%20sells%2080%20varieties%20of%20kitchenware%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20observed%20the%20artisans%E2%80%99%20work%20and%20how%20they%20were%20making%20utensils%2C%20and%20I%20realised%20something%20important%3A%20when%20you%20need%20to%20innovate%20a%20craft%2C%20you%20have%20to%20immerse%20yourself%20in%20it%20completely%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kirti%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20previously%20worked%20with%20craft%20clusters%2C%20she%20understood%20the%20process%20of%20collaborating%20with%20artisans.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%20working%20with%20them%20and%20learned%20about%20their%20skills%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20I%20had%20to%20adapt%20to%20their%20expertise%20to%20develop%20new%20products.%20One%20of%20our%20first%20new%20designs%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3Eparat%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20traditional%20flat%2C%20round%20utensil).%20We%20simply%20added%20a%20clock%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Eparat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20making%20it%20a%20functional%20and%20decorative%20piece.%20This%20design%20was%20easy%20for%20them%20to%20make%20because%20they%20were%20already%20accustomed%20to%20crafting%20%3Cem%3Eparats%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20initial%20days%20of%20her%20product%20making%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20very%20interesting%20for%20me%20as%20a%20designer%20to%20work%20with%20their%20skills%2C%20understand%20the%20market%2C%20and%20create%20something%20in%20collaboration%20that%20the%20market%20needed.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20learning%20and%20unlearning%20involved.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKirti%20says%20the%20products%20started%20to%20gain%20popularity%20after%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%20and%20people%20started%20to%20turn%20towards%20traditional%20and%20sustainable%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20attended%20exhibitions%20and%20gathered%20customer%20feedback.%20Through%20conversations%20and%20our%20experiences%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20during%20our%20first%20year%2C%20people%20didn%E2%80%99t%20fully%20understand%20our%20products.%20However%2C%20after%20about%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20we%20began%20to%20notice%20a%20genuine%20interest%20in%20purchasing%20our%20cookware%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20company%20produces%20over%2080%20types%20of%20products%20in%20kitchenware%2C%20dinnerware%20and%20tableware%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3Eparats%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20flat%20plate-like%20utensil%20used%20to%20kneed%20dough)%2C%20drinking%20glasses%2C%20tumblers%2C%20brass%20ladles%2C%20copper%20baking%20trays%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20collaborates%20with%20about%2050%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.