333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-2.34.38-PM_11zon-1720762380-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-2.34.38-PM_11zon-1720762380-1536x1023.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-2.34.38-PM_11zon-1720762380-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356665%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20picture%20of%20the%20bonded%20labourers%20as%20captured%20during%20the%20rescue%20operation%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Atul%20Kulkarni%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20feet%20were%20bruised%20and%20I%20could%20not%20move%20them.%20But%20still%2C%20I%20was%20expected%20to%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20maintains.%20One%20of%20the%20members%20involved%20in%20the%20rescue%20operation%20affirms%20this%2C%20on%20request%20of%20anonymity.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20police%20cracked%20down%20on%20the%20case%20and%20found%20Parth%2C%20his%20leg%20was%20rotting.%20The%20long%20hours%20of%20work%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20well%20water%20had%20worsened%20the%20condition.%20The%20police%20confirmed%20that%20if%20the%20rescue%20was%20even%20a%20little%20delayed%2C%20the%20leg%20would%20have%20to%20be%20amputated%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETreated%20like%20slaves%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParth%E2%80%99s%20story%20might%20spark%20a%20few%20questions%20in%20your%20mind%3B%20the%20first%20being%20about%20the%20ethicality%20of%20bonded%20labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20it%20still%20prevalent%3F%20Yes%2C%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%E2%80%9Cabolished%E2%80%9D%20is%20how%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Labour%20and%20Employment%20defines%20bonded%20labour%20%E2%80%94%20following%20the%20Bonded%20