0was%20going%20on.%20My%20team%20began%20checking%20the%20rooms%20on%20the%20property%20and%20on%20opening%20one%20of%20the%20doors%2C%20we%20saw%20the%20men%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kulkarni%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201052px)%20100vw%2C%201052px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-12.38.16-PM_11zon-1720762660.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221052%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IPS%20Officer%20Atul%20Kulkarni%20led%20the%20rescue%20operation%20that%20freed%20the%2011%20men%20along%20with%20seeing%20to%20their%20rehabilitation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-12.38.16-PM_11zon-1720762660.jpeg%201052w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-12.38.16-PM_11zon-1720762660-300x246.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-12.38.16-PM_11zon-1720762660-500x411.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-12.38.16-PM_11zon-1720762660-768x631.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-12.38.16-PM_11zon-1720762660-150x123.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356668%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIPS%20Officer%20Atul%20Kulkarni%20led%20the%20rescue%20operation%20that%20freed%20the%2011%20men%20along%20with%20seeing%20to%20their%20rehabilitation%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Atul%20Kulkarni%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppalled%20at%20the%20picture%20that%20met%20his%20eyes%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20hands%20and%20feet%20had%20been%20completely%20chained%20and%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20move.%20Their%20situation%20was%20pathetic%2C%20unimaginable%20for%20the%2021st%20century.%20They%20were%20all%20tied%20in%20one%20room%20with%20barely%20any%20food%20and%20water%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20Kulkarni%20and%20his%20team%20began%20the%20rescue%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20immediately%20removed%20the%20chains%20and%20set%20them%20free%2C%20but%20they%20were%20mentally%20wrecked.%20We%20could%20see%20the%20hopelessness%20in%20their%20eyes%3B%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20think%20help%20would%20ever%20come.%E2%80%9D%20What%20followed%20was%20a%20coming%20together%20of%20the%20social%20welfare%2C%20revenue%2C%20and%20labour%20departments%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%2011%20men%20were%20justly%20compromised%20for%20the%20unfair%20hand%20they%20had%20been%20dealt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParallelly%2C%20Kulkarni%20and%20his%20team%20conducted%20a%20raid%20targeted%20at%20nabbing%20every%20culprit%20with%20links%20to%20the%20case.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20easy%20to%20catch%20one%20or%20two%20people%20and%20brand%20it%20a%20success%20story.%20But%20in%20this%20case%2C%20nabbing%20the%20kingpin%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kulkarni%20explains%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20a%20well-thought-out%20hierarchy%20behind%20the%20operation.%20%E2%80%9CFurther%20probing%20led%20us%20to%20the%20network%20%E2%80%94%20recruiters%2C%20transporters%20who%20would%20take%20these%20labourers%20to%20designated%20places%2C%20employers%20who%20they%20were%20sold%20to%20%E2%80%94%20there%20were%20many%20layers%20to%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20was%20successful%20in%20nabbing%20all%20involved%2C%20followed%20by%20stringent%20booking%20under%20kidnapping%20and%20trafficking%20sections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fo-x0pxiE-r8%3Fsi%3DlFG2thjUYrKgHjkd%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20victims%20of%20bonded%20labour%20deserve%20more%20than%20freedom%2C%20the%20Government%20underscores.%20Rehabilitation%20is%20key%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20a%20way%20to%20ensure%20that%20these%20victims%20are%20not%20slaves%20to%20their%20past.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Labour%20and%20Employment%20suggests%20that%20out%20of%203%2C15%2C302%20people%20released%20from%20bonded%20labour%20between%201978%20and%202023%2C%20around%202%2C96%2C305%20persons%20have%20been%20rehabilitated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficer%20Kulkarni%20too%20saw%20to%20it%20that%20Parth%20and%20his%20compatriots%20were%20given%20skill%20development%20and%20training%2C%20and%20thus%20a%20bridge%20into%20the%20world%20of%20dignified%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20all%2011%20victims%20of%20the%20case%20have%20found%20hope%20in%20their%20newfound%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESevering%20crime%20at%20the%20root%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpotlighting%20the%20operation%E2%80%99s%20meticulous%20planning%2C%20Kulkarni%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20contractors%20had%20ensured%20that%20the%20families%20of%20these%20men%20didn%E2%80%99t%20guess%20what%20was%20up.%20They%20had%20conveyed%20a%20bogus%20story%20to%20them%2C%20assuring%20them%20that%20they%20were%20being%20well-rewarded%20for%20their%20work%20and%20would%20be%20returning%20home%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20the%20families%20were%20under%20the%20impression%20that%20the%20men%20were%20engaged%20in%20work%20and%20happy%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20too%20busy%20to%20keep%20in%20touch%20over%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnearthing%20this%20racket%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20simple%20feat.%20But%20if%20Kulkarni%E2%80%99s%20previous%20track%20record%20%E2%80%94%20as%20Addl.%20SP%2C%20Chandrapur%20(2022)%3B%20Addl.%20SP%20Gondia%20Camp%20Deori%20where%20he%20handled%20anti-Naxal%20operations%20(2019)%3B%20ASP%20in%20Thane%2C%20Maharashtra%20(2017-2019)%20%E2%80%94%20suggests%20anything%2C%20it%20is%20that%20his%20genius%20lies%20in%20cracking%20down%20on%20cases%20that%20would%20faze%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChallenges%20are%20no%20deterrent%20to%20his%20bravado.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20software%20engineer%20to%20now%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20law%20and%20order%20system%2C%20the%20digression%20has%20been%20intriguing.%20But%2C%20he%20sees%20it%20as%20fate.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20always%20inclined%20to%20work%20for%20society.%20During%20my%20urban%20planning%20course%20at%20the%20Tata%20Institute%20of%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20I%20worked%20in%20many%20slums%20and%20villages%20where%20I%20was%20exposed%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20social%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20apprehensive%20about%20whether%20he%20would%20be%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20governance%2C%20Kulkarni%20found%20inspiration%20in%20the%20officers%20he%20met%20along%20the%20way.%20At%2028%2C%20the%20young%20engineer%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20leap%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356313%2Fupsc-cse-ifs-officer-harsimran-singh-cheema-preparation-tips-strategy-forest-services%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappear%20for%20the%20UPSC%20exam%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20cleared%20it%20on%20the%20first%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Kulkarni%20has%20been%20breaking%20new%20ground%20with%20every%20project%20he%20undertakes.%20Early%20on%2C%20he%20understood%20that%20it%20is%20lack%20that%20leads%20to%20crime.%20His%20newest%20%E2%80%98Criminal%20Rehabilitation%E2%80%99%20project%20at%20the%20Dharashiv%20village%20is%20founded%20on%20this%20premise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPolicing%20and%20investigations%20are%20fine.%20But%20being%20a%20sociology%20student%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20inclined%20to%20look%20for%20the%20source%20of%20these%20deep%20problems%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kulkar